 Israels maßgebend? Welche Bedeutung kommt der Geschichte Israels zu?Dabei bewährt sich Wellhausens fundamentale Unterscheidung von „Judentum und altem Israel in ihrem Gegensatze“ und gewinnt überraschende Aktualität.   aThe History of Ancient Israel (1) describes of available sources on the history of Israel; (2) classifies the epochs in the history of Israel; (3) defines determinant structures in the history of Israel; (4) examines the significance of the history of Israel.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aJewsxHistory. 4aAlte Geschichte. 4aAlter Orient. 4aAltes Testament. 4aHistory of Israel. 4aIsrael. 4aOld Testament. 4aancient Near East. 4aancient history. 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2017z9783110548259oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831105305990 cprintz978311052999940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311053241840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110532418423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110532418.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017